class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">solution</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>routes<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  answer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n  routes<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>sort<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>key<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token keyword\">lambda</span> x<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> x<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># routes를 차량이 나간 지점(route[1]) 기준으로 정렬</span>\n  camera <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">30001</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># -30001부터 카메라 위치를 찾습니다.</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\"># 카메라가 진입시점(route[0])보다 작은지 확인합니다.</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\"># 작다면, 카메라를 한 개 더 세웁니다.</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\"># 최근 카메라의 위치를 갱신합니다.</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> route <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> routes<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> camera <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> route<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n          answer <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n          camera <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> route<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> answer</code></pre></div>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/category/algorithm/greedy/%EB%8B%A8%EC%86%8D%EC%B9%B4%EB%A9%94%EB%9D%BC/%EB%8B%A8%EC%86%8D%EC%B9%B4%EB%A9%94%EB%9D%BC/#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85\">문제 설명</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/category/algorithm/greedy/%EB%8B%A8%EC%86%8D%EC%B9%B4%EB%A9%94%EB%9D%BC/%EB%8B%A8%EC%86%8D%EC%B9%B4%EB%A9%94%EB%9D%BC/#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%A0%91%EA%B7%BC-%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D\">문제 접근 방식</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/category/algorithm/greedy/%EB%8B%A8%EC%86%8D%EC%B9%B4%EB%A9%94%EB%9D%BC/%EB%8B%A8%EC%86%8D%EC%B9%B4%EB%A9%94%EB%9D%BC/#%EC%B0%A8%EB%9F%89-%EB%8F%99%EC%84%A0%EC%9D%B4-%EC%B5%9C%EB%8C%80%ED%95%9C-%EB%A7%8E%EC%9D%B4-%EA%B2%B9%EC%B9%98%EB%8A%94-%EA%B5%AC%EA%B0%84%EC%97%90-%EC%B9%B4%EB%A9%94%EB%9D%BC%EB%A5%BC-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%98%EC%9E%90\">“차량 동선이 최대한 많이 겹치는 구간에 카메라를 설치하자”</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/category/algorithm/greedy/%EB%8B%A8%EC%86%8D%EC%B9%B4%EB%A9%94%EB%9D%BC/%EB%8B%A8%EC%86%8D%EC%B9%B4%EB%A9%94%EB%9D%BC/#%ED%92%80%EC%9D%B4-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C\">풀이 코드</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"[프로그래머스] 단속 카메라 - 그리디 알고리즘 / Python","description":"","date":"2020.06.11","emoji":"📸","category":"algorithm"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/category/algorithm/greedy/단속카메라/단속카메라/","relatedPosts":[{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/category/algorithm/competition/2018-kakao/뉴스클러스터링/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[프로그래머스] 뉴스 클러스터링 - [1차] 2018 카카오 / Python","date":"2020.06.05","emoji":"🌤","category":"algorithm"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/category/algorithm/competition/2018-kakao/n진수게임/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[프로그래머스] n진수 게임 - [3차] 2018 카카오 / Python","date":"2020.06.02","emoji":"🎮","category":"algorithm"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/category/algorithm/competition/2018-kakao/캐시/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[프로그래머스] 캐시 - [1차] 2018 카카오 / Python","date":"2020.05.30","emoji":"📚","category":"algorithm"}}}]}}}